                    "line_text": "Goulûment, salement, sans grand goût ni grand choix.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et j’inaugure aujourd’hui ce ruban de queues,",
